# Dhanashree Bhat — Portfolio (React + Vite)

A modern, animated personal portfolio website built with **React**, **Tailwind CSS**, **Framer Motion**, and **Lucide Icons**.

## Features

- **Hero section** with animated profile frame and typewriter role text
- **Scroll progress bar** at the top of the page
- **Mouse spotlight** background (soft radial glow following the cursor)
- **Tech Stack** skills with logo
- **Professional experience** with an interactive accordion (expand/collapse)
- **Education** cards
- **Projects** section with clickable repo links
- **Hobbies** with icon cards
- **Footer** with contact links

---

## Tech Stack

- React
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion
- lucide-react

---

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install

npm run dev
```
